==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stramash
<hw>Stram"ash</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>Stramazoun</er>.]</ety> <def>To strike, beat, or bang; to break; to
destroy.</def> <mark>[Scot. & Prov. Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stramash</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Stramash
<hw>Stram"ash</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A turmoil; a broil; a fray; a
fight.</def> <mark>[Scot. & Prov. Eng.]</mark>
<rj><au>Barham.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stramazoun</ent>⟦br⟧
